GasStorm orchestrates several external components, each distributed under its own
license by its respective project (pulled as Docker images or built from source;
see README.md):

  - block-builder, load-generator, privacy-proxy, block-explorer, chain-indexer
    (gateway-fm)
  - op-reth (Paradigm), cdk-erigon, agglayer / zkevm-bridge (Polygon),
    Hyperlane agent (Abacus/Hyperlane), Foundry/Anvil (Foundry), Besu (Hyperledger)

